main event: One round, white object, half the size of the spoke of a bicycle wheel, was observed rising and traveling toward the WSW in Seattle.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about 7-10 seconds, The object appeared to be going round and round, The sighting was reported as ascending at an angle of approximately 15 to 20 degrees, The object was described to look like a light on the spokes of a bicycle wheel, The conclusion drawn from the observation was that it was probably astronomical in nature.
